## Job Title
Java Developer with Spark and Scala

## Job Summary
We are seeking highly skilled and professional individual who can juggle both the complex world of Big Data frameworks (Spark, Hadoop, MapReduce) with their significant experience in Server Side Java applications.

## Required Skills
- Proficient in Java programming language including Spark and Scala Libraries;
- Strong knowledge in Linux including advanced concepts, filesystems, network and security;
- Understanding and ability to manage distributions specifically Red Hat Linux;
- Exceptional analytical problem-solving skills;
- Excellent troubleshooting and performance optimization of JVM, Analysis of Java dump files;

## Required Experience
Candidates should possess a minimum of:
- Five (5) years of experience of working as a Java Developer, specifically with Spark and Scala;
- Five (5) years of administration experience of Linux, more specifically Red Hat;

## Responsibilities
The Java Developer will need to:
- Develop and optimize Spark structured and streaming jobs that correlate data for analytic insights;
- Configure, tune, operate, and manage distributed computing environments, specifically on Red Hat Linux;
- Create technical documentations and specifications.
